data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to own this countryside sanctuary in Dayton. Situated on 5.625 acre lot, this 4-sided brick property boasts high ceilings, an open floor plan, tile flooring, a fireplace with a mosaic surround in the great room, formal dining room, game room, and a covered patio for outdoor entertaining and leisure. Take your culinary abilities to new heights in the gorgeous island kitchen, complete with granite countertops, a mosaic backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Find some peace and quiet in the relaxing master bathroom, featuring dual vanities, a whirlpool tub, and separate shower. Located near FM 1960 East with easy access to Atascocita and Baytown. Delve into premier shopping, dining, and entertainment at Atascocita Commons and Deerbrook Mall. Students attend Dayton ISD. This is the home of your dreams - call today!
